At We Are Empower, we believe that empowerment is not a one - way process , it is a shared journey of growth, inclusion, and
transformation. Our mission is to reach the most vulnerable and marginalized sections of society, not with sympathy, but with
tools, knowledge, and confidence to help them lead dignified, independent lives. We exist to ignite self-belief and unlock the
potential that already exists in every person, especially in rural areas and underserved communities.
Our vision is to build a society where no dream is too big, and no background is too small. We believe that real change happens
when opportunities are made accessible to all regardless of caste, gender, location, or economic background. Through skill
development, educational support, digital awareness, and confidence building programs, we are creating sustainable change at
the grassroots level.
One of the pillars of our work is skill development under the Government of India’s Skill India Mission. We proudly facilitate
access to free, government-certified courses for youth and women, ensuring that every participant not only learns a skill but
also gains lifelong support through consulting, technical help, and confidence building. We charge only a minimal registration
and management fee to keep these programs running effectively and transparently.
Our NGO operates with a holistic approach. Along with education and skilling, we conduct workshops, health awareness
camps, digital literacy drives, women self-help initiatives, and career guidance programs. We work with schools, panchayats,
local communities, and young volunteers to ensure that our mission reaches every corner where help is needed.
But what truly sets We Are Empower apart is our belief in partnership. The name itself , We Are Empower is not just about the
beneficiaries. It’s about every volunteer, supporter, trainer, and well-wisher who walks this journey with us. We are not giving
power to others; we are awakening the power within them together.
We are not here to simply create dependency through charity. We aim to create changemakers people who can rise above their
circumstances and go on to uplift others. This ripple effect is the heartbeat of our foundation.
To all those who have supported us so far and to those who wish to join hands in the future: your contribution—whether time,
resources, or skills , can help transform lives. Let us unite in this movement to create a more empowered, educated, and self-
reliant India.
Together, We Are Empower
Warm regards,
Vaibhav Thakur , Gujarat

TYPES OF WAE
WAE Academy ensures Education for All, while the Digital Academy
equips youth with modern skills. The Medical Wing spreads health
awareness and care. WAE Organization Committee manages planning
and execution across india.
The Art Academy, Color Studio, and Creative Team nurture creativity,
while THYNK WAE drives innovation. Environment Project , WAE
promotes green living and sustainability. The State Teams mobilize local
impact across regions.
WAE also conducts live events, operates WAE Collections for identity-
driven merchandise, and supports learning through WAE Consulting and
Editing Team services. The Administrative Wing ensures strong internal
governance, while the Elite Club honors excellence in service.
Together, these units form a powerful movement that uplifts
communities, especially the underprivileged, through knowledge, action,
and unity. We Are Empower is more than an NGO , it’s a mission to
transform India, one life at a time.
